There's a lot of cars I always wanted. But for a long time, I decided that if I could only have one, it would be an Outback.

Now that I was out of school and gainfully employed, I fulfilled that lifelong dream.

Then I packed up my crap (including my drone(s)!), threw it in the car, and took the I-80. Maybe I'll write a trip log later?
